The paper describes a new clinical literature search engine that utilizes a ranking algorithm to filter non-medical journals, compare semantic similarity between queries, and incorporate journal impact factor and publication date. This suggests that the paper may fall under the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Deep Learning (cs.DL), Cybernetics (cs.CY), or Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories.
